REQUIREMENTS:

    * click
    * tabulate


USAGE:

The setup script creates two entry points.

ts-editor: Used to edit topics from the command line.
ts-selector: Used to select topics or read a list of topics.

---
Usage: ts-editor [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...

Options:
  --help  Show this message and exit.

Commands:
  create              Creates a new topic [TOPIC] [DESCRIPTION]
  delete              Deletes a topic by [TID]
  update              Updates a topic [TID] [TOPIC] [DESCRIPTION]
  update-description  Updates a topic [TID] [DESCRIPTION]
  update-topic        Updates a topic [TID] [TOPIC]
---

---
Usage: ts-selector [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...

Options:
  --help  Show this message and exit.

Commands:
  read
  select
---
